Follow `AGENTS.md` for all Carousel OS workflows. This is a local AI-agent workspace, not a website project.

When creating carousels, read the hook system, brand design system, and brand config before generating slides. Render with `createCarousel()` and report the output folder.

When publishing, use Postiz only after `.env` and brand integration IDs are configured. Never expose secrets.
